## PATH ALIASES
- `@/` → `src/` (frontend)
- `@shared/` → `shared/` (shared types)

## PRISMA SCHEMA CONVENTION
```prisma
model Asset {
  id         Int     @id @default(autoincrement())
  kodeAset   String  @unique @map("kode_aset")   // camelCase di code
  namaBarang String  @map("nama_barang")         // snake_case di DB
  
  @@map("assets")
}
```

Setelah edit schema:
```bash
cd backend
pnpm run prisma:format
pnpm run prisma:generate
```
